        <div xml:id="TK149">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>nalakkuriyār yāreṉi ṉāmanīr vaippiṟ</l>
<l>piṟaṟkuriyā ṭōṭōyā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it asked, "who are those who shall obtain good in this world surrounded by the terror-producing sea ?" Those who touch not the shoulder of her who belongs to another.</l>
            </lg>
